title: Kenai River Baseline Water Quality Project Data QA/QC Years 2014 - 2023
text:
Preface
This document is the online work-in-progress for preparation of data that will be used in the upcoming report, Water Quality Assessment of the Kenai River Watershed, 2000 - 2023.
Downloads
This report can also be downloaded as an Microsoft Word document by clicking on the ‘W’ symbol in the upper left corner. When the report is complete, it will be available to download as a PDF.
Github
All project files and source code are hosted in a public GitHub repository, which is accessible by clicking the GitHub symbol in the upper left corner.
This online report is not optimized for use on mobile devices, and is best accessed on a desktop or laptop computer.
